title: Who’s to blame for terrorism? Terrorists.
text:
Donald Trump attends a boxing match in New York on Oct. 17. (Associated Press/Rich Schultz, File) (Rich Schultz/AP) By Eugene Robinson Opinion writer October 19 at 8:09 PM Follow @Eugene_Robinson Is Jeb Bush justified in claiming his brother “kept us safe” from terrorism? Obviously not.
